thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by SM

author: SM
title: SM
text:
On arrival: Quick access, no long lines compared to the big brand rentals.
great clean modern car with USB charger built in (able to use google maps from my iPhone).
Affordable.
great service
On return: quick and easy. filled petrol before I returned the car, and just dropped off the keys at the counter.
